                <h3 data-uuid="4b1d67cbf6254c00b145987c0684a883">French Indochina</h3>
            </article>
            <figure class="image" data-uuid="d306865fb8ea4118a8d043e397a4fbe6">
                <img alt="This map shows the colony of French Indochina in the late 1800s. The colony includes the countries of Vietnam, Laos, and Cambodia. " data-uuid="79e8deb0c0a44a2094072a9a187d7552" src="../../img/module_29_lesson01/ms_snlese454149_702m.png" />
                <div class="figcaption" data-uuid="cf6264581a61480ea4632877c08f9999">
                    <p class="caption" data-uuid="25e7fa8afe7242a481dbeb205a1f3cf0">France combined its protectorates of Laos, Cambodia, and Vietnam in 1891 to create French Indochina.</p>
                </div>
