                <h2 data-uuid="a46ca37f85da4caf939770b309589b4e">The Beginning of the Vietnam War</h2>
                <p data-uuid="5f285ea14eec42dd8816db624c3900da">Many of the causes of the Vietnam War revolve around the simple belief held by many Americans that communism was threatening to expand throughout southeast Asia. Brutal and corrupt governments in both North and South Vietnam also escalated tensions.</p>
            </article>
